caption: This image displays a hand holding a blue metal mechanical pencil. The hand is holding the pencil near the middle with the thumb and index finger, and the pencil is pointed at a piece of white paper with printed text. There is a small smudge of graphite on the paper where the pencil tip touched it. In the background is a white table with placemats and fake green plants. The pencil is blue and made of metal with a ribbed grip. The paper has black ink printed on it, and the text is written in a Times New Roman font. The image is a photograph taken from a close-up angle. The hand holding the pencil is relaxed, conveying a sense of casualness. The overall tone of the image is calm and studious. There are no other objects present in the image.
